Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.09,0:18:31.46,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}All I need is fight
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.46,0:18:35.51,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}All I gotta find is the way to be a survivor
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.51,0:18:37.30,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It's quite simple thing
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.30,0:18:41.01,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Pull the trigger on the enemy
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.01,0:18:42.31,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}There's no time to lose
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.31,0:18:43.85,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Suicide or shoot
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.85,0:18:46.56,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Cuz no such a nonsense "right or wrong"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.56,0:18:49.69,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Ain't no way to ever understand
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:55.86,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}How I do enjoy this GAME
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.16,0:19:06.96,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Over there, live and die, fight for some reasons
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.96,0:19:09.50,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Let me join and let's have party!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:12.63,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Before my coffee gets cold
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.63,0:19:14.88,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.88,0:19:19.60,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Roll your dice again
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.47,0:19:24.39,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Time to do a bet
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.06,0:19:26.27,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Shouting for the pain
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.27,0:19:27.56,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Sounds like quite insane
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:30.61,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}That is how I recognize life
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.61,0:19:35.90,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No matter what situation pull the trigger
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.90,0:19:37.32,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Nothing else matters,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:38.49,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Lovers or haters
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.49,0:19:40.07,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Bring the gun on my head
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.07,0:19:44.54,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}So I can concentrate on my target
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.54,0:19:50.54,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And win this GAME! Hell oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.09,0:19:55.51,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The more they are in good condition
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.51,0:19:58.51,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The more I can be damn so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.51,0:20:03.68,IN JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Are you ready to fly?
